āIn recognition of all who suffer from domestic abuse
in North Somerset and to mark the U.N. Day of Action
Against Violence against women and children.
Women's Project 25.11.2003

Don't suffer violence in silence CALL 0800-69-49-999
for free confidential support and advice
The Domestic Abuse FreeFone support line (DAFFS)
Offers a single point of contact for free and confidential
advice and support to any person suffering domestic abuse
Call now, protect yourself and anyone you suspect may be suffering"ć
